Package: philcore
Title: Core Data Structures for Phil Ecosystem
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Yusuke", "Matsui", email = "mail.to.matsui@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides core data structures for the Phil philosophy research
    ecosystem. Includes PhilCorpus (a SummarizedExperiment-like container for
    philosophical texts), ConceptSpans (GRanges-like concept annotations), and
    PhilCollection (multi-corpus integration). Designed for cross-cultural,
    multilingual philosophical text analysis.
